RxKotlin revolves around the Observable type that represents a system of real-life events and data, 's
now break these things down sequentially to understand it better:
1) Observer subscribes to Observable
2) Observable starts emitting the items that it has in it
3) Observer reacts to whatever item the Observable emits

== Learn concept of RX from https://medium.freecodecamp.org/rxandroid-and-kotlin-part-1-f0382dc26ed8
